                    "type": "sidebar",
                    "text": "Every 5,000 years, the mightiest of the cornugons is chosen to rise to the station of malebranche, a form of lesser divinity just below that of the archdevils. Currently 12 members of the malebranche are known to exist, and while each exhibits unique forms of depravity and wickedness, all share the same goal of conquering the Material Plane.",
